article_title: Heh! Ex-MTV VJ Kennedy nails it with Obamacare pre-existing condition question – twitchy.com
article_text:
Snort!

Enter ex-MTV VJ Kennedy, who wonders if something else is an Obamacare-covered pre-existing condition.

Is ignorance a pre-existing condition? — Kennedy (@KennedyNation) December 3, 2013

Dead-on snark.

This Twitter user hammers the sad truth home:

@KennedyNation Yes. And sadly the only one some people want to keep rather than cure. — Drew (@drucifus) December 3, 2013
